  3.8133380782342987`*^9, 3.813338096941387*^9}, {3.813338350638522*^9, 
  3.813338353057596*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"95c7da96-e379-4789-894f-\
0547790dc9fa"],

Cell["\<\
Perform out - of - core data analysis on terabyte - scale datasets.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.774785883246394*^9, 
  3.7747859056897383`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"60235226-1f2c-47f7-b986-\
07d8f98543b3"],

Cell["\<\
Compile common Wolfram Language syntax into arbitrary type - safe SQL \
expressions.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.774785883246394*^9, 
  3.774785911900724*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7e74541d-be00-4167-ab66-\
465e16f166ab"],

Cell["Construct and manipulate queries symbolically.", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.774785883246394*^9, 
  3.774785916537435*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"944a89b4-2f6b-49e2-9a23-\
02fe4ba85bff"],

Cell["\<\
Go hybrid : Perform large - scale data manipulation in SQL and finer analyses \
in the Wolfram Language.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.774785883246394*^9, 
  3.774785919809585*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5f4d5499-3e66-40d8-891a-\
179dc0db0575"]
