Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "SlideShowNavigationBar",
 CellTags->
  "SlideShowHeader",ExpressionUUID->"d71f3087-c2e2-4028-a4fa-6c21a2c4bff8"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Connecting to a local MySQL server (in your computer), and doing read - write \
operations\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775466801646418*^9, 3.7754668242742367`*^9}, {
  3.7792844215231247`*^9, 3.779284449747004*^9}, {3.77928540288815*^9, 
  3.779285403154416*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"472b1619-75c8-4912-91d7-\
620b64ec6271"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Full documentation in ",
 ButtonBox["DatabaseLink User Guide",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://reference.wolfram.com/language/DatabaseLink/tutorial/\
Overview.html"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://reference.wolfram.com/language/DatabaseLink/tutorial/Overview.\
html"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775467831995669*^9, 
  3.7754678551349*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9c3fbe4c-02df-474b-bb16-b62fb82e4fa0"],

Cell["\<\
DatabaseLink is a Wolfram Language application that provides a set of tools \
allowing convenient integration of the Wolfram Language with database \
management systems.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775467857983629*^9, 3.775467880385553*^9}, {
  3.775468092231083*^9, 
  3.775468102628077*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2c4cbeaf-83cc-4ac4-bc0a-\
ef9e33abe597"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Features of DatabaseLink", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775467857983629*^9, 3.775467880385553*^9}, {
  3.775468092231083*^9, 
  3.775468106188283*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"182f3f61-2283-434b-9057-\
ea66a32332de"],

Cell["\<\
Connectivity\[Dash]works with most standard SQL database applications and \
with databases that are local and network based (including different types of \
computers). You can connect to virtually any standard SQL database that \
provides a JDBC (Java Database Connectivity) driver. \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 3.775468146361739*^9}, {
  3.9803999300682583`*^9, 
  3.980399932904244*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7adec0d8-3285-420e-a879-\
84006f69d8aa"],

Cell["\<\
Supplied drivers\[Dash]built\[Hyphen]in support for many important databases, \
including MySQL, PostgreSQL, Open Database Connectivity (ODBC), Firebird, and \
HSQLDB, H2 and Derby etc...\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 3.7754681559043612`*^9}, {
  3.775468202879747*^9, 3.7754682028801813`*^9}, {3.980399936505488*^9, 
  3.980399952768937*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"398253a9-a199-4aca-ae0d-\
d1c7cb3e6a04"],

Cell["\<\
 SQL command interface\[Dash]you can exploit your knowledge of SQL without \
learning a new system.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 3.7754681559043612`*^9}, {
  3.7754682039880867`*^9, 
  3.7754682099364557`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2b36ec41-dea9-4dc2-977d-\
d0966e1b5767"],

Cell["\<\
The Wolfram Language command interface\[Dash]useful if you are familiar with \
Wolfram Language programming.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 3.7754681559043612`*^9}, {
  3.7754682039880867`*^9, 
  3.775468212543901*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7b430874-1b4f-4970-89fc-\
549805519a1b"],

Cell["\<\
GUI interfaces\[Dash]the Database Explorer and the Connection Tool provide \
convenient tools for opening connections and querying the database.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 
  3.775468168599122*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3ea2771e-fddb-45c7-b942-\
05540b703aab"],

Cell["\<\
Access to data and metadata\[Dash]you can inspect the names of tables and \
columns, as well as the data in each entry.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 
  3.775468184821972*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e05e51bb-8fae-45c9-bcaf-\
17a1f37125e9"],

Cell["\<\
Data type support\[Dash]works with standard SQL data types, including \
numbers, strings, binary data, date and time, and Wolfram Language \
expressions.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775468126847423*^9, 
  3.775468184987644*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9565055b-dcfb-4cbf-9a52-\
66ea072075de"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "SlideShowNavigationBar",
 CellTags->
  "SlideShowHeader",ExpressionUUID->"6a971c69-fb85-40e2-9e8c-a7a21d9a02a4"],

Cell["The Command-Line Interface To connect to SQL Database", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.77546837208409*^9, 3.775468376135036*^9}, {
  3.77554581998123*^9, 
  3.775545827508183*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d4572c41-5dd6-4639-bda4-\
51348aa18cc2"],

Cell["\<\
Many users of DatabaseLink will have an existing database they wish to \
connect to and use. If you do not already have a database, you can use \
HSQLDB, SQLite, H2, Oracle, or Derby (all included in DatabaseLink).\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.77554987380132*^9, 3.775549902033308*^9}, {
  3.813473510564447*^9, 
  3.81347351284673*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"11af54e5-3954-4f34-b632-\
3ca892f6f7a2"],

Cell["\<\
The command-line interface is a powerful and flexible interface that is \
particularly appropriate if you want to write programs that use database \
functionality\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.77554987380132*^9, 
  3.775549901707712*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d51c806c-44dc-4669-b5b7-\
0f5ca086432f"],

Cell["\<\
DatabaseLink is a Wolfram Language add - on application. Before any functions \
from the package can be used, it must be loaded as follows :\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.77546841920477*^9, 3.775468449894159*^9}, 
   3.7755499106303864`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"b7c10a54-e33d-4f31-8a30-\
6ca481f0d212"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Needs", "[", "\"\<DatabaseLink`\>\"", "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.77546844410656*^9, 3.775468444109496*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[108]:=",ExpressionUUID->"14a0c136-e8e1-4ff5-b7be-9e46ce45fb14"],

